general.gigTitle: do website development and be your full stack web developer

sellerCard.oneLiner: We are a website development and digital marketing company
sellerCard.description: At Corammers we deliver end-to-end website development and digital marketing services to help brands succeed online. We build professional business websites, dynamic e-commerce platforms, and custom software solutions. Our digital marketing services include social media management, Google Ads, SEO, and email marketing. As CRM specialists, we also offer GoHighLevel solutions to enhance lead generation and customer retention, providing a powerful foundation for your digital growth.

description.content:
Hi, I'm Junaid, a professional web developer with 8 years of experience and created over 200 websites for various industries. Now, as the founder of Corammers, my agency is dedicated to providing exceptional web development services based on client's requirements.


Expertise


I offer a wide range of website development services, including:


  • Designing and building complete business websites , eCommerce development solutions and landing pages
  • Converting designs from Figma to HTML and Figma to WordPress.
  • Speed optimization for a faster and smoother user experience.
  • Creating scalable and secure eCommerce websites tailored to your needs.


With proficiency in WordPress, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Python, and PHP, my team can handle even the most complex projects efficiently.


Why Me?

  • Personalized Solutions: I understand your business, challenges, and goals, ensuring clear communication through Zoom meetings to deliver work that meet your unique needs.
  • Client Satisfaction: My clients consistently praise my communication skills and dedication to delivering high-quality results.


Lets build something extraordinary together!


Please contact me before placing the order

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many revisions i get?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Client satisfaction is my top priority, and I offer unlimited revisions to ensure the final result aligns perfectly with your vision. While we’ll follow the initial requirements as our foundation, I am committed to making any necessary adjustments to deliver exceptional results.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can i get website maintenance services too?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do provide website maintenance services in a very reasonable price.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you help me to setup domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will help you to setup your domain and hosting and I will make you website live on your domain and hosting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can i expect marketing services after the website is done?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, We do provide marketing services as well and we can discuss about your marketing plan.

reviews.comment:
Working with Junaid was and is an absolute pleasure. He and his service are not only very responsive, but they go above and beyond in making sure that they understand in depth what your gig is.

This, in our professional opinion is severely lacking not only on Fiverr but in other companies that you can find that are not on Fiverr.

Our company is listed on Trustpilot and is a member in good standing with the United States Chamber of Commerce and the PA Chamber of Commerce and Industry. As such, it is imperative that we utilize a Fiverr professional who can meet our expectations and uphold our stellar reputation.

Junaid and his company accomplished this and is the reason why we're satisfied.

I want to share that the company has been respectful and invested in the project. We worked together pretty effortlessly, and Corammers did a great job communicating throughout the project. There are still some bugs in the project that I have recently found out, but I feel confident that they will still correct them. I am more than happy to work with them again!

seller_response.comment: thank you sir and yeah we will definitely fix if there is any issue 🙂

reviews.comment: It was amazing working with Junaid. He was willing to jump on a call and talk through the nuisances of my website. His work was very good and it was wonderful working with him.

Corammors was a pleasure to work with, they were quick to work, understood the job and all in all a great help with any and everything that needed to be done, will forever sure be working with them again!
Once again very good work and very happy with the results and process working with corammers
